M#S_1X22.NAME: 1X2 2UP
M#S_1X22.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the match in 90 minutes. If the team you selected takes a two-goal lead at any point during the match, your selection will be settled as a winner.

M#S_1X21.NAME: 1X2 1UP
M#S_1X21.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the match within 90minutes. If the team you selected takes a one-goal lead at any point during the match, your selection will be settled as a winner.

M#GS_CARDYESNO.NAME: Show A Card Yes/No
M#GS_CARDYESNO.DESC: Predict whether the player will be shown a Card Yes/No.

M#GS_CD.NAME: Cards Duo
M#GS_CD.DESC: You have to predict if your selected player or his substitute will be shown a yellow or red card during the match.

M#GS_STP.NAME: Shots Target Plus
M#GS_STP.DESC: You must predict whether the total number of shots on target taken or  a wood or crossbar hit by a selected player or his substitute during the match will be higher or lower than the spread offered.

M#GS_SD.NAME: Shots Duo
M#GS_SD.DESC: You have to predict whether the total number of shots made by a selected player or his substitute during the match will be over or under the spread offered

M#GS_ST.NAME: Shots on Target
M#GS_ST.DESC: You have to predict whether the total number of shots on target made by a selected player during the match will be over or under the spread offered.

M#GS_A.NAME: AssistDuo
M#GS_A.DESC: You have to predict if the selected player or his substitute will record an assist during the match

M#GS_STD.NAME: Shots on Target Duo
M#GS_STD.DESC: You have to predict whether the total number of shots on target made by a selected player or his substitute during the match will be over or under the spread offered.

M#GS_1STSCORER.NAME: First Goalscorer
M#GS_1STSCORER.DESC: You predict that the selected player will score the first goal of the match

M#GS_LASTSCORER.NAME: Last Goalscorer
M#GS_LASTSCORER.DESC: You have to predict that the selected player will score the last goal of the match

M#GS_ANYGPLMIN.NAME: Anytime Goal Player Minutes
M#GS_ANYGPLMIN.DESC: You have to predict the minute interval that your selected player will score a goal.

M#GS_ANY1H.NAME: Any 1H
M#GS_ANY1H.DESC: You have to predict whether the selected player will score anytime in the 1st half only. The player must start the match for the bet to be valid

M#GS_AD.NAME: Anytime Duo
M#GS_AD.DESC: You have to predict whether the selected player or his substitute will score at least one goal.

M#GS_1P.NAME: 1st Plus
M#GS_1P.DESC: You have to predict whether the selected player or his substitute will score the first goal or hit a wood or crossbar first in the match

M#GS_NGOALS.NAME: N. Goals
M#GS_NGOALS.DESC: You have to predict that the selected player will score at least two goals or three goals during the match

M#GS_ANYSCORER.NAME: Anytime
M#GS_ANYSCORER.DESC: You have to predict that the selected player will score at least one goal during the match. There are two possible outcomes, YES (the selected player will score at least one goal in the match) and NO (the player will not score a goal in the match). The selected player must start the match or the bet will be void

M#GS_1STSCORER.NAME: First Goalscorer
M#GS_1STSCORER.DESC: You predict that the selected player will score the first goal of the match

M#S_1X21ST10MIN.NAME: 1X2 - 10 Minutes
M#S_1X21ST10MIN.DESC: Which team will win the first ten minutes of the match?

M#S_WINMARGIN.NAME: Winning Margins
M#S_WINMARGIN.DESC: By how many goals will a team win the match?

M#S_HTFTCS.NAME: HT / FT Correct Score
M#S_HTFTCS.DESC: Correct score prediction for half time and full time.

M#S_1X21ST5MIN.NAME: 1X2 - 5 Minutes
M#S_1X21ST5MIN.DESC: Which team will win the first five minutes of the match?

M#S_1X21ST15MIN.NAME: 1X2 - 15 Minutes
M#S_1X21ST15MIN.DESC: Which team will win the first fifteen minutes of the match?

M#S_1X21ST20MIN.NAME: 1X2 - 20 Minutes
M#S_1X21ST20MIN.DESC: Which team will win the first twenty minutes of the match?

M#S_PENSCOREMISS.NAME: Penalty Scored/Missed
M#S_PENSCOREMISS.DESC: Will there be a penalty scored/missed?

M#S_1X21ST30MIN.NAME: 1X2 - 30 Minutes
M#S_1X21ST30MIN.DESC: 1X2-30min You have to predict the outcome of the first ten (30) minutes. There are three possible outcomes: 1 (the home team wins), X (the teams draw), 2 (the away team wins).

M#S_1X21ST60MIN.NAME: 1X2 - 60 Minutes
M#S_1X21ST60MIN.DESC: 1X2-60min You have to predict the outcome of the first ten (60) minutes. There are three possible outcomes: 1 (the home team wins), X (the teams draw), 2 (the away team wins).

M#S_GIT.NAME: Goal Injury Time
M#S_GIT.DESC: You have to predict whether there will be a goal scored in injury time or not. (Not including extra time).

M#S_PEN.NAME: Penalty
M#S_PEN.DESC: You have to predict if there will be a penalty awarded during the match

M#S_1STGHT.NAME: Half 1st Goal
M#S_1STGHT.DESC: You have to predict in which half will be scored the first goal of the match.

M#S_SCORET.NAME: Team To Score
M#S_SCORET.DESC: You have to predict which team will score during the match

M#S_LEASTX.NAME: At Least a Half X
M#S_LEASTX.DESC: You have to predict if there will be at least a half which ends with a draw (regarding the second half, without considering the score acquired during the first half)

M#S_GOALTYPE.NAME: First Goal Method
M#S_GOALTYPE.DESC: You have to predict what type of goal the first goal of the match will be by the selected player, or in the selected match

M#S_EXT12.NAME: Qualify In ExtraTime
M#S_EXT12.DESC: You have to predict which team will qualify after the Extra Time period. If this is the final of the given tournament, you are predicting which team will lift the trophy after the Extra Time period

M#S_EXT12P.NAME: Qualify On Penalties
M#S_EXT12P.DESC: You have to predict the team that will win the match at the end of the penalty shootout

M#S_EXTPENALTY.NAME: Penalty Shoot Out
M#S_EXTPENALTY.DESC: You have to predict whether the match will be decided by a penalty shootout scenario

M#S_EXT1X2.NAME: 1X2 Only Extra Time
M#S_EXT1X2.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the extra time of the match. If the game ends before extra time the bets will be voided

M#S_EXTOU.NAME: O/U Only Ex.Time
M#S_EXTOU.DESC: You have to predict whether the total goals scored in the Extra Time period will be under or over the spread indicated. If the game ends before extra time the bets will be voided

M#S_OUBOOK.NAME: Over/Under Cards
M#S_OUBOOK.DESC: Total number of bookings given during the match in regular time (FT).

M#S_OUBOOK1T.NAME: 1st Half - Over/Under Cards
M#S_OUBOOK1T.DESC: You have to predict if the amount of cards in the first half will be over or under the indicated spread

M#S_OEBOOK.NAME: Odd/Even Cards
M#S_OEBOOK.DESC: Odd or even total number of booking after Full time (FT)

M#S_REDCARD.NAME: Red Card
M#S_REDCARD.DESC: You have to predict if one or more players will be sent off during the match

M#S_1X2BOOK.NAME: 1X2 Cards
M#S_1X2BOOK.DESC: Predict which team will receive the most bookings during the game during regular time. A yellow card has value of 1 point, a red card has value of 2 points. When a player is sent off because of being shown two yellow cards, a maximum of 3 points will be considered (yellow card + red card).

M#S_OUBOOKHOME.NAME: Home cards Over/Under
M#S_OUBOOKHOME.DESC: You have to predict how many bookings will be made by the home team.

M#S_1X2BOOK1T.NAME: 1st Half - Cards
M#S_1X2BOOK1T.DESC: Which team will receive the most bookings during the first half?

M#S_EXACTBOOK.NAME: Exact Cards
M#S_EXACTBOOK.DESC: The exact number of total bookings for both teams given during the match.

M#S_OUBOOKAWAY.NAME: Away cards Over/Under
M#S_OUBOOKAWAY.DESC: You have to predict how many bookings will be made by the away team.

M#S_1STBOOK.NAME: First Card 1X2
M#S_1STBOOK.DESC: You have to predict which team the first card of the match will be awarded to

M#S_LASTBOOK.NAME: Last Card 1X2
M#S_LASTBOOK.DESC: Wich team will receive  the last booking in normal play?

M#S_2HTOUCA.NAME: 2nd Half - Over/Under Cards
M#S_2HTOUCA.DESC: You have to predict if the amount of cards in the second half will be over or under the indicated spread.

M#S_REDCARD1T.NAME: Red Card  Half Time
M#S_REDCARD1T.DESC: You have to predict if one or more players will be sent off during the first half of the match

M#S_RCH.NAME: Red Card Home
M#S_RCH.DESC: You have to predict if one or more players of the home team will be sent off during the match, including overtime.

M#S_RCA.NAME: Red Card Away
M#S_RCA.DESC: You have to predict if one or more players of the away team will be sent off during the match, including overtime.

M#S_BOOKSHOME.NAME: Number Cards Home
M#S_BOOKSHOME.DESC: The total number of booking points achieved by the home team at full time.

M#S_BOOKSAWAY.NAME: Number Cards Away
M#S_BOOKSAWAY.DESC: The total number of booking points achieved by the away team at full time.

M#S_HMC.NAME: Half Most Card
M#S_HMC.DESC: You have to predict which half of the match will contain the most bookings

M#S_ECH.NAME: Exact Cards HT
M#S_ECH.DESC: You have to predict the exact number of cards awarded during the first half period only.

M#S_BTLC.NAME: Both teams least Cards
M#S_BTLC.DESC: Both teams will be awarded cards during the match

M#S_CAH1.NAME: Cards Asian Handicap
M#S_CAH1.DESC: You have to predict the final two-way result of the match on Cards taking into account the handicap offered.

M#S_C15M.NAME: Cards 15 Minutes
M#S_C15M.DESC: You must predict whether a card will be awarded in the first 15 minutes of the match.

M#S_C30M.NAME: Cards 30 Minutes
M#S_C30M.DESC: You must predict whether a card will be awarded in the first 30 minutes of the match.

M#S_MULTIC1.NAME: Multi Cards
M#S_MULTIC1.DESC: It is necessary to predict which selection of cards will contain the correct score for the match.

M#S_FCH1.NAME: First Card HT
M#S_FCH1.DESC: You have to predict which team will be awarded the first card in the first half

M#S_HNDCORNER.NAME: Corner Handicap
M#S_HNDCORNER.DESC: What will the result be after the allotted Corner Handicap is applied to the corner score

M#S_CORNERSHOMEOU.NAME: Home Corner Over/Under
M#S_CORNERSHOMEOU.DESC: You have to predict how many corners will be made by the home team.

M#S_CORNERSAWAYOU.NAME: Away Corner Over/Under
M#S_CORNERSAWAYOU.DESC: You have to predict how many corners will be made by the away team.

M#S_MULTIC.NAME: Multi Corner
M#S_MULTIC.DESC: One must predict whether the number of corners taken in the match is within the indicated range.

M#S_MULTICH1.NAME: Multi Corner HT
M#S_MULTICH1.DESC: You must predict whether the number of corners taken in the first half is within the indicated range.

M#S_FCH.NAME: First Corner HT
M#S_FCH.DESC: You have to predict which team will be awarded the first corner in the first half

M#S_LCH.NAME: Last Corner HT
M#S_LCH.DESC: You have to predict which team will be awarded the last corner in the first half.

M#S_OECH.NAME: Odd/Even Corner HT
M#S_OECH.DESC: You must predict whether the total number of corners taken in the first half is an even or odd number.

M#S_CAH.NAME: Corner Asian Handicap
M#S_CAH.DESC: You have to predict the team who takes the most corners in the match taking into consideration the handicap spread offered.

M#S_CAHH.NAME: Corner Asian Handicap HT
M#S_CAHH.DESC: You have to predict the team who takes the most corners in the first half of the match taking into consideration the handicap spread offered.

M#S_CAH2.NAME: Corner Asian Handicap 2HT
M#S_CAH2.DESC: You have to predict the team who takes the most corners in the second half of the match taking into consideration the handicap spread offered.

M#S_CHH.NAME: Corner Handicap HT
M#S_CHH.DESC: You have to predict the team who takes the most corners in the first half taking into consideration the handicap spread offered.

M#S_CH2.NAME: Corner Handicap 2HT
M#S_CH2.DESC: You have to predict the team who takes the most corners in the second half taking into consideration the handicap spread offered

M#S_1STCORNER.NAME: First Corner
M#S_1STCORNER.DESC: You have to predict which team will be awarded the first corner of the match. Three possible outcomes: 1 (the home team is awarded the first corner of the match), None (no corners are awarded during the match) and 2 (the away team is awarded the first corner of the match).

M#S_OUCORNERS.NAME: Corner - Over/Under
M#S_OUCORNERS.DESC: Will the match have more or less corners than the allotted Total line during normal time?

M#S_TEAMCORNER.NAME: 1X2 Corner
M#S_TEAMCORNER.DESC: Which team will get the most corners during the game in normal play?

M#S_OECORNER.NAME: Corner Odd/Even
M#S_OECORNER.DESC: Odd or even total number of corners at full time.

M#S_LASTCORNER.NAME: Last Corner
M#S_LASTCORNER.DESC: You have to predict which team will be awarded the final corner in the match. Three possible outcomes: 1 (the home team is awarded the final corner of the match), X (no corners are awarded during the match) and 2 (the away team is awarded the final corner of the match).

M#S_CORN10.NAME: Corner 10 Minutes
M#S_CORN10.DESC: You have to predict whether a corner will be taken by either team in the first 10mins of the match only (First 10mins = 0:00 - 9:59 on the match clock)

M#S_TEAMCORNER1T.NAME: 1st Half - 1X2 Corner
M#S_TEAMCORNER1T.DESC: You have to predict which team will have more corners in the first half (1X2).

M#S_1X2C2HT.NAME: 2nd Half - 1X2 Corner
M#S_1X2C2HT.DESC: You have to predict which team will have more corners in the second half (1X2).

M#S_C1HTOU.NAME: 1st Half - Corner Over/Under
M#S_C1HTOU.DESC: You have to predict if the total amount of corners in the first half of the match will be over or under the total spread (Over/Under).

M#S_C2HTOU.NAME: 2nd Half - Corner Over/Under
M#S_C2HTOU.DESC: You have to predict if the total amount of corners in the second half of the match will be over or under the total spread (Over/Under).

M#S_CORNERHTFT.NAME: Corners HT/FT
M#S_CORNERHTFT.DESC: You have to predict which team will have the most corners in the first half of the match together with team that has the most corners when the match is completed

M#S_HALFCORNER.NAME: Half Most Corner
M#S_HALFCORNER.DESC: You have to predict which half of the match there will be more corners.

M#S_ST.NAME: 1X2 Shots on Target
M#S_ST.DESC: You have to predict which team will have the most number of shots on target in the match. Settled using Opta data.

M#S_STOU.NAME: O/U Shots on Target
M#S_STOU.DESC: You have to predict whether the total amount of shots on target in the match will be over or under the spread offered. Settled using Opta data.

M#S_STHOU.NAME: O/U Home Shots on Target
M#S_STHOU.DESC: You have to predict whether the total amount of shots on target in the match by the home team only will be over or under the spread offered. Settled using Opta data.

M#S_STAOU.NAME: O/U Away Shots on Target
M#S_STAOU.DESC: You have to predict whether the total amount of shots on target in the match by the away team only will be over or under the spread offered. Settled using Opta data.

M#S_1X2SHOTS.NAME: 1X2 Shots
M#S_1X2SHOTS.DESC: You have to predict which team will have the most number of shots in the match. Settled using Opta data.

625479556$S_DCH1X2FT_1X2.M_NAME: Double Chance Half Time/1X2 Full Time

625479556$S_DCH1X2FT_121.M_NAME: Double Chance Half Time/1X2 Full Time

625479556$S_DCH1X2FT_12X.M_NAME: Double Chance Half Time/1X2 Full Time

625479556$S_DCH1X2FT_X22.M_NAME: Double Chance Half Time/1X2 Full Time

M#S_CHANCEMIXGGOU.NAME: Chance Mix
M#S_CHANCEMIXGGOU.DESC: Bet on a combination outcome of events. If one of the events occurs, your bet is a winner. eg. selection 1or3+ - if the home team wins or there are 3 or more goals in the match, the bet is a winner.

M#S_CHANCEMIX.NAME: 1X2 Or Goal/No Goal
M#S_CHANCEMIX.DESC: You have to predict the winning outcome of the match OR whether both, one or nether teams will score in the match.

M#S_CHANCEMIXOU.NAME: 1X2 or Over/Under
M#S_CHANCEMIXOU.DESC: Bet on a combination outcome of events. If one of the events occurs, your bet is a winner. eg. selection 1or3+ - if the home team wins or there are 2 or more goals in the match, the bet is a winner.

M#S_DCHTFT.NAME: Double Chance Half Time/Full Time
M#S_DCHTFT.DESC: Bet on the double chance result of both the 1st half and second half.

M#S_3CM.NAME: 1X2 Or Goal/No Goal Or Over/Under
M#S_3CM.DESC: Bet on a combination outcome of events. If one of the events occurs, your bet is a winner. eg. selection 1 or GG or Ov - if the home team wins or or both team score or there are 2 or more goals in the match, the bet is winner.

M#S_3COMBO1.NAME: 1X2 + Goal/No Goal + Over/Under
M#S_3COMBO1.DESC: Bet on a combination of events in the match. All three outcomes must happen for your bet to win.

M#S_DCMULTI4-5.NAME: DC & Multi Goal 4-5
M#S_DCMULTI4-5.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the double chance plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 4-5

M#S_GGNGOUN.NAME: GG/NG & Over/Under 3.5
M#S_GGNGOUN.DESC: You have to predict the combination of both teams to score or not (GG/NG) plus the total goals scored will be over or under the indicated spread

M#S_HTFTOU.NAME: HT/FT & O/U
M#S_HTFTOU.DESC: You have to predict the halftime-fulltime result plus the total goals will be over or under the indicated spread

M#S_1X2HDCFT.NAME: 1X2 Half Time/Double Chance Full Time
M#S_1X2HDCFT.DESC: You have to predict the halftime result together with 3 possible double chance outcomes (1X, 12 & X2) of the match (Excluding extra time).

M#S_DCH1X2FT.NAME: Double Chance Half Time/1X2 Full Time
M#S_DCH1X2FT.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the match with 3 possible double chance outcomes (1X, 12 & X2) at the halftime together with the outcome of the match (extra time excluded).

M#S_HTFTOUHT.NAME: HT/FT & O/U 1,5 HT
M#S_HTFTOUHT.DESC: You have to predict the halftime-fulltime result plus the total goals in the first half will be over or under the indicated spread.

M#S_MATCHOVERFLOW.NAME: First Goal & 1X2
M#S_MATCHOVERFLOW.DESC: You have to predict together if the final result of the match will be 1, X or 2 and which team will score the first goal of the match

M#S_HTFTOU.NAME: HT/FT & O/U
M#S_HTFTOU.DESC: You have to predict the halftime-fulltime result plus the total goals will be over or under the indicated spread

M#S_CHANCEMIXOU.NAME: 1X2 or Over/Under
M#S_CHANCEMIXOU.DESC: Bet on a combination outcome of events. If one of the events occurs, your bet is a winner. eg. selection 1or3+ - if the home team wins or there are 2 or more goals in the match, the bet is a winner.

M#S_1X2HTGGNG.NAME: 1st Half - 1X2 & Goal/No Goal
M#S_1X2HTGGNG.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the first half and whether both teams will score or not in the first half only. 1 & GG = Home win and both teams score X & GG = Draw and both teams score 2 & GG = Away win and both teams score 1 & NG = Home win and only one or neither teams score X & NG = Draw and only one or neither teams score 2 & NG = Away win and only one or neither teams score

M#S_DCOU.NAME: Double Chance & Over/Under
M#S_DCOU.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the match and whether the total goals scored in 90mins will be over or under the spread indicated

M#S_DCGGNG.NAME: Double Chance & Goal / No Goal
M#S_DCGGNG.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the match & whether both teams will score in 90mins or not. 1X & GG = Home win or draw and both teams score 12 & GG = Home or away win and both teams score X2 & GG = Draw or away win and both teams score 1X & NG = Home win or draw and only one or neither teams score 12 & NG = Home or away win and only one or neither teams score X2 & NG = Draw or away win and only one or neither teams score

M#S_DCGGNGHT.NAME: 1st Half - Double Chance & Goal/No Goal
M#S_DCGGNGHT.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the first half and whether both teams will score or not in the first half only. 1X & GG = Home win or draw and both teams score 12 & GG = Home or away win and both teams score X2 & GG = Draw or away win and both teams score 1X & NG = Home win or draw and only one or neither teams score 12 & NG = Home or away win and only one or neither teams score X2 & NG = Draw or away win and only one or neither teams score

M#S_DCGGNG2T.NAME: 2nd Half - Double Chance & Goal/No Goal
M#S_DCGGNG2T.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the second half and whether both teams will score or not in the second half only. 1X & GG = Home win or draw and both teams score 12 & GG = Home or away win and both teams score X2 & GG = Draw or away win and both teams score 1X & NG = Home win or draw and only one or neither teams score 12 & NG = Home or away win and only one or neither teams score X2 & NG = Draw or away win and only one or neither teams score

M#S_2HT1X2GGNG.NAME: 2nd Half - 1X2 & Goal/No Goal
M#S_2HT1X2GGNG.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the second half and whether both teams will score or not in the second half only. 1 & GG = Home win and both teams score X & GG = Draw and both teams score 2 & GG = Away win and both teams score 1 & NG = Home win and only one or neither teams score X & NG = Draw and only one or neither teams score 2 & NG = Away win and only one or neither teams score

M#S_HTDCOU.NAME: 1st Half - Double Chance & Over/Under
M#S_HTDCOU.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the first half and whether the total goals scored  will be over or under the spread indicated

M#S_2TDCOU.NAME: 2nd Half - Double Chance & Over/Under
M#S_2TDCOU.DESC: You have to predict the outcome of the second half and whether the total goals scored  will be over or under the spread indicated

M#S_1X2MULTI1-2.NAME: 1X2 & Multi Goal 1-2
M#S_1X2MULTI1-2.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the final result plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 1-2

M#S_DCMULTI1-2.NAME: DC & Multi Goal 1-2
M#S_DCMULTI1-2.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the double chance plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 1-2

M#S_1X2MULTI1-3.NAME: 1X2 & Multi Goal 1-3
M#S_1X2MULTI1-3.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the final result plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 1-3

M#S_DCMULTI1-3.NAME: DC & Multi Goal 1-3
M#S_DCMULTI1-3.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the double chance plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 1-3

M#S_1X2MULTI1-4.NAME: 1X2 & Multi Goal 1-4
M#S_1X2MULTI1-4.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the final result plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 1-4

M#S_DCMULTI1-4.NAME: DC & Multi Goal 1-4
M#S_DCMULTI1-4.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the double chance plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 1-4

M#S_1X2MULTI2-3.NAME: 1X2 & Multi Goal 2-3
M#S_1X2MULTI2-3.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the final result plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 2-3

M#S_1X2MULTI2-4.NAME: 1X2 & Multi Goal 2-4
M#S_1X2MULTI2-4.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the final result plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 2-4

M#S_1X2MULTI3-4.NAME: 1X2 & Multi Goal 3-4
M#S_1X2MULTI3-4.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the final result plus if the range of total goals scored during the match will be between 3-4

M#S_1X2OU.NAME: 1X2 & Over/Under
M#S_1X2OU.DESC: You have to predict the whether the outcome of the match will be 1,X or 2 and also whether the total goals scored will be over or under

M#S_1X2GGNG.NAME: 1X2 & Goal/No Goal
M#S_1X2GGNG.DESC: You have to predict together if the final result of the match will be 1, X or 2 and if both teams will score at least one goal each during the whole match (GG) or one or both the teams do not score any goal during the whole match (NG)

M#S_1X2HTOU.NAME: 1st Half - 1X2 & Over/Under
M#S_1X2HTOU.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the first half time result and whether the total number of goals scored in the first half will be over or under the spread indicated.

M#S_GGNGOU.NAME: Goal/No Goal & Over/Under
M#S_GGNGOU.DESC: You have to predict together if both teams score and the number of goals scored during the match will be over or under the spread indicated

M#S_1X22TOU.NAME: 2nd Half - 1X2 & Over/Under
M#S_1X22TOU.DESC: You have to predict the combination of the second half time result and whether the total number of goals scored in the second half will be over or under the spread indicated.
